Justification: \
- ST ecosystem + supported by Arduino libraries \
- 6 axis IMU (3-axis accelerometer, 3-axis gyroscope) with digital I2C/SPI interface\
-low power consumption\
- integrated sensor fusion and programmable finite state machine (FSM) , reducing MCU processing load and enabling more advanced motion features without firmware complexity\
- high performance, widely used so lots more documentation\
- configurable ranges (2-16g acule, up to 4000dps gyro) to support low noise precision sensing, high-dynamic applications\
- low-power \'93always on\'94 operation\
- large FIFO - enables buffering of motion data, reducing MCU interrupt load and allowing more efficient data handling\
\
