\f1\b0\fs26 \cf0 SDA (P1.04) and SCL (P1.05) pullups to 3.3V are DNP. I2C bus pullups are provided by the onboard 4.7K resistors on the HS91L02W2C01 display module (confirmed from module schematic, page 8, R6 and R7). \
These serve the entire bus including the LSM6DSV IMU. \
Footprints retained on PCB for flexibility in case display is replaced with a module lacking onboard pullups. \
Distance from pullup to MCU is not a concern at this PCB scale \'97 total trace length across the entire bus is under 30mm with only two devices, making capacitive effects negligible. \
4.7k\uc0\u937  is sufficient to meet the 300ns maximum rise time specified in the display datasheet (page 11, AC characteristics).
